          "username": "francistoth"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2020-04-17 12:23:44.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 15:\n\nHi,\n\nCould you please review these changes? They refer to SDC-2499, which fixes many of the problems related to the testing of asdctool. It is part of a topic which goal is to separate the report writing and formatting logic to improve maintainability and testability.\n\nThis change adds unit test for ValidationConfigManager as required by SDC-2499. ReportManager has been deleted as showed by the previous changes, and therefore do not longer require any unit tests. The next changes will focus on code formatting, test coverage increase and some refactoring related to the ArtifactToolBL class.\n\nThank you in advance,\n\nFrancis",
        "patchset_number": 15
      },
      {
        "id": "892170f0e68351422bf0c9eee6bc9b4136862a6f",
